OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FAny residual
OL,6,Fshowers quickly fading to leave a dry
OL,7,Fnight with long clear spells, and
OL,8,Fwinds becoming generally light.
OL,9,FTurning widely cold with a slight
OL,10,Ffrost developing in places.
OL,11,
OL,12,CMonday:FAfter a chilly start, a dry
OL,13,Fday follows with variable cloud but
OL,14,Falso bright spells, with some hazy
OL,15,Fsunshine possible later. Generally
OL,16,Flight winds and temperatures rising
OL,17,Fabove average.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
